divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking outside to go to work when I looked up to see the airplane I heard. The something weird caught my eye. It was a translucent ob j ect so far up in the sky I kept losing sight of it in the sky . It didn't maneuver it just went in a straight line. The video camera on my phone didn't pick it up. Then finally I just couldn't find in in the sky again. The full event lasted 30 seconds or so.
